Ask HN: How long could Twitter operate if the remaining staff quit?
text:
In almost every organization there are roles that could be trimmed, but it seems extreme that Twitter is potentially laying off half the company today.

Can the company survive that? If the remaining team is over worked or feels like they are not respected… what would happen if they all left en mass?

Show HN: Curational.xyz – On-demand generative AI, curated by pros
text: I found that using Generative AI platforms like DALLE-2 and Midjourney was tricky and time-consuming - it takes ages, and the right prompt, to get what you want. So I built this curation platform, where you can ask a professional creator to curate you the best output from Generative AI platforms, given what you want. I'd love any feedback from the community on whether it's useful / what I should change!
